3867
02:30:03,640 --> 02:30:04,960
And another thing too,

3868
02:30:05,120 --> 02:30:06,320
that very little indeed

3869
02:30:06,320 --> 02:30:07,620
is necessary for living

3870
02:30:07,620 --> 02:30:08,500
a happy life.

3871
02:30:08,780 --> 02:30:11,060
And because thou hast despaired

3872
02:30:11,060 --> 02:30:12,600
