3873
02:30:12,600 --> 02:30:14,660
and skilled in the knowledge of nature,

3874
02:30:15,200 --> 02:30:16,340
do not for this reason

3875
02:30:16,340 --> 02:30:17,240
renounce the hope

3876
02:30:17,240 --> 02:30:19,200
of being both free and modest,

3877
02:30:19,680 --> 02:30:21,900
and social, and obedient to God.

3878
02:30:22,220 --> 02:30:23,500
It is in thy power

3879
02:30:23,500 --> 02:30:25,580
