4057
02:35:15,190 --> 02:35:16,430
Alexander and Gaius

4058
02:35:16,430 --> 02:35:17,410
and Pompeius,

4059
02:35:17,850 --> 02:35:18,450
what are they

4060
02:35:18,450 --> 02:35:19,110
in comparison

4061
02:35:19,110 --> 02:35:20,110
with Diogenes

4062
02:35:20,110 --> 02:35:21,030
and Heraclitus

4063
02:35:21,030 --> 02:35:21,850
and Socrates?

4064
02:35:26,700 --> 02:35:27,860
But as to the others,

4065
02:35:28,160 --> 02:35:28,900
how many things

4066
02:35:28,900 --> 02:35:30,120
had they to care for

4067
02:35:30,120 --> 02:35:31,200
and to how many things

4068
02:35:31,200 --> 02:35:32,200
were they slaves?

4069
02:35:33,640 --> 02:35:34,500
Consider that men

4070
02:35:34,500 --> 02:35:35,640
will do the same things

4071
02:35:35,640 --> 02:35:36,320
nevertheless,

4072
02:35:36,720 --> 02:35:37,400
even though thou

4073
02:35:37,400 --> 02:35:38,160
shouldst burst.

4074
02:35:38,700 --> 02:35:39,920
This is the chief thing.

4075
02:35:40,160 --> 02:35:41,140
Be not perturbed,

4076
02:35:41,200 --> 02:35:41,820
for all things

4077
02:35:41,820 --> 02:35:42,360
are according

4078
02:35:42,360 --> 02:35:42,940
to the nature

4079
02:35:42,940 --> 02:35:43,680
of the universal,

4080
02:35:44,040 --> 02:35:45,280
and in a little time

4081
02:35:45,280 --> 02:35:45,940
thou wilt be

4082
02:35:45,940 --> 02:35:46,380
nobody

4083
02:35:46,380 --> 02:35:47,040
and nowhere.

4084
02:35:48,200 --> 02:35:49,360
In the next place,

4085
02:35:49,600 --> 02:35:50,800
having fixed thy eyes

4086
02:35:50,800 --> 02:35:52,260
steadily on thy business,

4087
02:35:52,760 --> 02:35:53,580
look at it,

4088
02:35:53,740 --> 02:35:55,060
and at the same time,

4089
02:35:55,140 --> 02:35:55,960
remembering that

4090
02:35:55,960 --> 02:35:56,920
it is thy duty

4091
02:35:56,920 --> 02:35:58,140
to be a good man,

4092
02:35:58,500 --> 02:35:59,440
and what man's

4093
02:35:59,440 --> 02:36:00,340
nature demands,

4094
02:36:00,940 --> 02:36:01,500
do that

4095
02:36:01,500 --> 02:36:02,800
without turning aside.

4096
02:36:08,620 --> 02:36:10,200
The nature of the universal

4097
02:36:10,200 --> 02:36:11,420
has this work to do,

4098
02:36:11,820 --> 02:36:13,380
to remove to that place

4099
02:36:13,480 --> 02:36:15,020
the things which are in this,

4100
02:36:15,240 --> 02:36:16,400
to change them,

4101
02:36:16,880 --> 02:36:17,840
to take them away.

4102
02:36:21,880 --> 02:36:23,300
You need to add some text

4103
02:36:23,300 --> 02:36:24,180
for me to talk.

4104
02:36:25,050 --> 02:36:26,630
Every nature is contented

4105
02:36:26,630 --> 02:36:27,290
with itself

4106
02:36:27,290 --> 02:36:29,330
when it goes on its way well,

4107
02:36:29,910 --> 02:36:31,150
and a rational nature

4108
02:36:31,150 --> 02:36:32,650
goes on its way well.

4109
02:36:33,380 --> 02:36:34,560
When in its thoughts

4110
02:36:34,560 --> 02:36:35,820
it ascends to nothing

4111
02:36:35,820 --> 02:36:37,020
false or uncertain,

4112
02:36:37,580 --> 02:36:38,660
and when it directs

4113
02:36:38,660 --> 02:36:39,260
its movements

4114
02:36:39,260 --> 02:36:40,780
to social acts only,

4115
02:36:41,280 --> 02:36:42,420
and when it confines

4116
02:36:42,420 --> 02:36:44,240
its desires and aversions

4117
02:36:44,240 --> 02:36:45,040
to the things

4118
02:36:45,040 --> 02:36:46,380
which are in its power,

4119
02:36:48,230 --> 02:36:50,370
everything that is assigned to it

4120
02:36:50,370 --> 02:36:51,530
by the common nature,

4121
02:36:52,310 --> 02:36:53,430
you need to add some text

4122
02:36:53,430 --> 02:36:54,350
for me to talk.

4123
02:36:55,230 --> 02:36:56,810
For of this common nature

4124
02:36:56,810 --> 02:36:58,690
every particular nature

4125
02:36:58,690 --> 02:36:59,490
is a part,

4126
02:37:00,050 --> 02:37:01,630
as the nature of the leaf

4127
02:37:01,630 --> 02:37:03,190
is a part of the nature

4128
02:37:03,190 --> 02:37:04,050
of the plant,

4129
02:37:08,240 --> 02:37:09,420
intelligent and just,

4130
02:37:09,660 --> 02:37:10,860
since it gives to everything

4131
02:37:10,860 --> 02:37:11,700
in equal portions,

4132
02:37:11,920 --> 02:37:12,940
and according to its worth,

4133
02:37:13,240 --> 02:37:14,160
times, substance,

4134
02:37:14,360 --> 02:37:15,400
cause, form,

4135
02:37:15,880 --> 02:37:16,280
activity,

4136
02:37:16,660 --> 02:37:17,220
and incident.

4137
02:37:17,880 --> 02:37:19,940
All things are familiar to us,

4138
02:37:19,940 --> 02:37:21,540
but the distribution of them

4139
02:37:21,540 --> 02:37:22,860
still remains the same.

4140
02:37:23,180 --> 02:37:24,000
But examine,

4141
02:37:24,420 --> 02:37:25,220
not to discover

4142
02:37:25,220 --> 02:37:26,280
that any one thing

4143
02:37:26,280 --> 02:37:28,060
compared with any other single thing

4144
02:37:28,060 --> 02:37:29,700
is equal in all respects,

4145
02:37:30,040 --> 02:37:31,280
but by taking all the parts

4146
02:37:31,280 --> 02:37:32,460
together of one thing

4147
02:37:32,460 --> 02:37:33,520
and comparing them

4148
02:37:33,520 --> 02:37:34,680
with all the parts together

4149
02:37:34,680 --> 02:37:35,200
of another.

