5020
03:33:58,580 --> 03:34:04,340
into some nook where thou shalt maintain them, or even depart at once from life,

5021
03:34:04,680 --> 03:34:11,300
not in passion, but with simplicity and freedom and modesty, after doing this one

5022
03:34:11,300 --> 03:34:15,920
laudable thing, at least in thy life, to have gone out of it thus.

5023
03:34:16,760 --> 03:34:23,660
You need to add some text for me to talk. In order, however, to the remembrance of these names,

5024
