03:34:51,960 --> 03:35:03,140
torpor, slavery, will daily wipe out those holy principles of thine, but it is thy duty,

5028
03:35:03,520 --> 03:35:08,440
so to look on and so to do everything, that at the same time the power of dealing with

5029
03:35:08,440 --> 03:35:15,440
circumstances is perfected, and the contemplative faculty is exercised, and the confidence which

5030
03:35:15,440 --> 03:35:20,020
comes from the knowledge of each several thing is maintained without showing it,

5031
03:35:20,020 --> 03:35:25,060
but yet not concealed. You need to add some text for me to talk.

5032
03:35:25,840 --> 03:35:31,480
For when wilt thou enjoy simplicity, when gravity, and when the knowledge of every

5033
03:35:31,480 --> 03:35:38,730
several thing, both what it is in substance, and what place it has in the universe,

5034
03:35:39,640 --> 03:35:44,280
and how long it is formed to exist, and of what things it is compounded,

5035
03:35:44,940 --> 03:35:50,780
and to whom it can belong, and who are able both to give it, and take it away.

5036
03:35:51,440 --> 03:35:56,100
