5038
03:36:02,070 --> 03:36:12,970
boars, and another when he has taken bears. Are not these robbers, if thou examinest

5039
03:36:12,970 --> 03:36:20,150
their opinions? Acquire the contemplative way of seeing how all things change into one another,

5040
03:36:20,410 --> 03:36:25,850
and constantly attend to it, and exercise thyself about this part of philosophy,

5041
03:36:31,440 --> 03:36:37,640
for nothing is so much adapted to produce magnanimity. Such a man has put off the

5042
03:36:37,640 --> 03:36:43,740
body, and as he sees that he must, no one knows how soon go away from among men,

5043
03:36:43,740 --> 03:36:50,430
and leave everything here. He gives himself up entirely to just doing in all his actions,

5044
03:36:50,790 --> 03:36:55,150
and in everything else that happens he resigns himself to the universal nature.

5045
03:36:59,190 --> 03:37:02,790
