5046
03:37:03,030 --> 03:37:08,270
he never even thinks of it being himself contented with these two things, with acting

5047
03:37:08,270 --> 03:37:12,950
justly in what he now does, and being satisfied with what is now assigned to him,

5048
03:37:12,950 --> 03:37:18,910
and he lays aside all distracting and busy pursuits, and desires nothing else than to

5049
03:37:18,910 --> 03:37:24,270
accomplish the straight course through the law, and by accomplishing the straight course to

5050
03:37:24,270 --> 03:37:33,390
follow God. What need is there of suspicious fear, since it is in thy power to inquire

5051
03:37:33,390 --> 03:37:41,720
what ought to be done? And if thou seest clear, go by this way content, without turning back.

5052
03:37:43,350 --> 03:37:51,090
But if any other things oppose thee, go on according to thy powers with due consideration,

5053
03:37:51,590 --> 03:37:56,750
keeping to that which appears to be just. For it is best to reach this object,

5054
03:37:56,950 --> 03:38:00,870
and if thou dost fail, let thy failure be in attempting this.

5055
03:38:01,350 --> 03:38:07,170
He who follows reason in all things, is both tranquil and active at the same time.

5056
03:38:12,930 --> 03:38:19,110
Now hast not forgotten, I suppose, that those who assume arrogant heirs in bestowing their praise

5057
03:38:19,110 --> 03:38:25,430
or blame on others, are such as they are at bed, and at board, and now hast not forgotten

5058
03:38:25,430 --> 03:38:31,490
what they do, and what they avoid, and what they pursue, and how they steal, and how they

5059
03:38:31,490 --> 03:38:39,680
rob, not with hands and feet, but with their most valuable part, means of which there is

5060
03:38:39,680 --> 03:38:48,500
When a man chooses, fidelity, modesty, truth, law, a good demon, happiness, it will make no

5061
03:38:48,500 --> 03:38:55,020
difference. To her who gives and takes back all, to nature, the man who is instructed and

5062
03:38:55,020 --> 03:39:03,570
modest says, Give what thou wilt, take back what thou wilt. Short is the little which remains

5063
03:39:03,570 --> 03:39:10,630
