5064
03:39:10,630 --> 03:39:16,780
or here, if he lives everywhere in the world, as in a state, political community.

5065
03:39:17,640 --> 03:39:22,120
Let men see. Let them know a real man, who lives according to nature.

5066
03:39:25,980 --> 03:39:29,240
Constantly contemplate the whole of time and the whole of substance,

5067
03:39:29,660 --> 03:39:34,160
and consider that all individual things as to substance are a grain of a fig,

5068
03:39:34,460 --> 03:39:40,600
and as to time the turning of a gimlet. Look at everything that exists, and observe that it

5069
03:39:40,600 --> 03:39:45,940
is already in dissolution and in change, and as it were putrefaction or dispersion,

5070
03:39:46,120 --> 03:39:51,600
or that everything is so. Consider what men are when they are eating, sleeping,

5071
03:39:52,000 --> 03:39:57,330
generating, easing themselves, and so forth. Then what kind of men they are when they are

5072
03:39:57,330 --> 03:40:02,830
imperious and arrogant, or angry and scolding from their elevated place, but a short time

5073
03:40:02,830 --> 03:40:08,610
ago, to how many they were slaves, and for what things, and after a little time consider

5074
03:40:08,610 --> 03:40:17,950
what a condition they will be. And it is for its good, at the time when nature brings it.

5075
03:40:21,730 --> 03:40:26,670
