5077
03:40:35,570 --> 03:40:40,790
or thou art going away, and this was thy own will, or thou art dying, and hast

5078
03:40:40,790 --> 03:40:47,350
discharged thy duty. But besides these things, there is nothing. Be of good cheer then.

5079
03:40:47,350 --> 03:40:52,830
Let this always be plain to thee, that this piece of land is like any other,

5080
03:40:53,110 --> 03:40:57,710
and that all things here are the same, with things on top of a mountain,

5081
03:40:57,870 --> 03:41:04,730
